column5: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EVecRi_DgnE  something to get the morning started  Peter
Holy Crap!!!! That'll wake you up in the morning!!
Saw that this morning. Was pretty funny when he said holy cow
Yikes!  Don't know why that's funny....  ....But I laughed! Lol
Seen that on the National last night.  Crazy..
saw it last night also and figured I'm safe so long as I don't venture to Africa.  if you listen closely, which I didn't hear yesterday, I think the lead says look at the donkey and points at it.
I know a few Afrikaners. Dem doods is crazy!
OUUCHHH !!! thank god it wasnt a lion or Cheetah chasing that beast The story woulda had a different ending
Don't know how well a helmet would hold up to a Impala in this country.Since they weight about two ton.
wow ... lucky for that guy the horns were turned upwards and didn't impale him ... what are the chances of that happeneing on a bike ride ?
His odds in Africa, are way better then mine in central Ontario.
you think that's bad, I had a samsquatch do the same thing to me - flying dropkick, one hairy foot to the face (thank goodness he used his foot)
have to ride faster i guess.
did ya get a picture? If not, it never happened
What the heck.....That is madness. Like flying along in a bass boat and having a sturgeon jump out of the water and take you out!!
